    <item>
      <title>美国零售销售增速为三个月来最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/us-retail-sales-rise-at-strongest-pace-in-three-months-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[商务部数据显示，未经通货膨胀因素调整的零售采购价值增长了 0.6%，全面上涨。不包括汽车，销售额增长 0.4%。迈克·麦基报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-17/us-retail-sales-rise-at-strongest-pace-in-three-months-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 14:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳从官方债权人那里获得了2026年之前的债务延期偿付</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/ghana-wins-debt-moratorium-until-2026-from-official-creditors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳已赢得官方债权人暂停偿付债务至 2026 年 5 月的请求，并预计将在 3 月底前与欧洲债券投资者达成协议，重组 130 亿美元的债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/ghana-wins-debt-moratorium-until-2026-from-official-creditors</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 11:30:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
